column2: select p.ID , po.objId as x_id, p.ra, p.dec, o.distance*# as d_arcsec , case when po.raErr > po.decErr then po.raErr else po.decErr end as pos_err , po.u, po.g, po.r, po.i, po.z into Nway_input_scs_DR1# from MyDB.Nway_input p cross apply dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (p.ra, p.dec, #) o join photoobj po on po.objid = o.objid order by distance
